    "Description": "This is an Idol Pop × Rock remix of the Japanese graduation classic “Tabidachi no hini (旅立ちの日に).”\nOriginally composed by Hiromi Takahashi (then music teacher, maiden name Sakamoto) and written by Noboru Kojima (then principal) in 1991,\nthe song has become one of the most beloved graduation anthems in Japan.\nThis remix is made with full respect to the original creators and the timeless message of farewell and new beginnings.\n\nPerfect for graduation season, farewells, and moments of new challenges.\nI hope this remix brings both nostalgia and excitement to listeners around the world.\n\n#TabidachiNoHini #GraduationSong #Idol #Jpop #旅立ちの日に",
